---
import Page from '../../layouts/Page.astro';
---

<Page
  title="AI-Enhanced Services"
  description="AI tools integrated into real production workflows. Batch processing, render correction, ComfyUI pipelines, rapid concept variations. Vision Graphics Kft."
>
  <div class="service-page">

    <div class="service-breadcrumb">
      <a href="/services/">Services</a>
      <span>→</span>
      <span>AI-Enhanced Services</span>
    </div>

    <p class="section-label">Service</p>
    <h1 class="display-lg service-h1">AI-Enhanced Services</h1>
    <p class="service-tagline-large">Useful AI. Not hype.</p>

    <p class="service-lead">
      We've integrated AI tools into our actual production workflow — not as a demo,
      but because it makes real projects faster and better. We'll also tell you where
      AI doesn't help. Not every problem needs an AI solution.
    </p>

    <hr class="service-rule" />

    <div class="service-body-grid">
      <div class="service-main">

        <h2 class="service-section-h2">What we actually do with AI</h2>
        <div class="deliverable-grid">
          {[
            {
              title: 'Rapid Concept Variations',
              desc: 'ComfyUI / SwarmUI pipelines generate material, lighting, and design variations quickly — so you can explore options without full re-renders for each.',
            },
            {
              title: 'Batch Image Processing',
              desc: 'Automated pipelines for processing large render batches: colour correction, format conversion, watermarking, and quality checks at scale.',
            },
            {
              title: 'AI-Assisted Render Correction',
              desc: 'Upscaling, noise reduction, and detail enhancement on existing renders. Useful for repurposing older project imagery.',
            },
            {
              title: 'Automated File Organisation',
              desc: 'Custom scripts and AI-assisted tools for organizing, naming, and cataloguing large visual archives.',
            },
            {
              title: 'Inpainting & Compositing',
              desc: 'Precise AI-assisted inpainting for removing unwanted elements, filling in details, or extending compositions.',
            },
            {
              title: 'Style Exploration',
              desc: 'AI-generated mood references to explore visual direction before committing to full 3D production.',
            },
          ].map(d => (
            <div class="deliverable-card">
              <h3 class="deliverable-title">{d.title}</h3>
              <p class="deliverable-desc">{d.desc}</p>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>

        <h2 class="service-section-h2">Our honest position</h2>
        <p class="body-text">
          AI tools genuinely accelerate some parts of visualization work — concept
          exploration, batch processing, and certain types of image correction.
          They don't replace 30 years of 3D expertise, scene-building knowledge,
          or understanding of what makes a render actually communicate something.
        </p>
        <p class="body-text">
          We integrate AI where it reduces time and cost without compromising quality.
          We'll tell you which parts of your project will benefit and which won't.
        </p>

        <h2 class="service-section-h2">Tools we use</h2>
        <div class="tools-list">
          {['ComfyUI', 'SwarmUI', 'Stable Diffusion', 'ControlNet', 'Topaz AI', 'Python automation', 'Custom MAXScript pipelines'].map(t => (
            <span class="tool-tag">{t}</span>
          ))}
        </div>

      </div>

      <aside class="service-sidebar">
        <div class="sidebar-block">
          <h3 class="sidebar-label">Pricing</h3>
          <p class="sidebar-price">By scope</p>
          <p class="sidebar-note">AI-enhanced work is typically priced as an add-on to a standard project, or as a standalone batch job. Quote on request.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="sidebar-cta">
          <a href="/contact/" class="btn btn-primary sidebar-btn">Get a Quote</a>
          <a href="/vision-tech/" class="btn btn-ghost">Our tech stack</a>
        </div>
      </aside>
    </div>

  </div>
</Page>

<style>
  .service-page { max-width: 1060px; }
  .service-breadcrumb { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem; font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: 0.72rem; color: var(--color-text-faint); margin-bottom: 2rem; }
  .service-breadcrumb a { color: var(--color-text-muted); text-decoration: none; transition: color 200ms; }
  .service-breadcrumb a:hover { color: var(--color-accent); }
  .service-h1 { margin: 0.5rem 0 0.75rem; }
  .service-tagline-large { font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 1.2rem; font-style: italic; color: var(--color-accent); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
  .service-lead { font-size: 0.98rem; color: var(--color-text-muted); max-width: 65ch; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0 0 2rem; }
  .service-rule { border-color: var(--color-border); margin-bottom: 2.5rem; }
  .service-body-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 240px; gap: 4rem; align-items: start; }
  .service-main { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 2.5rem; }
  .service-section-h2 { font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: 0.65rem; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 0.15em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--color-text-faint); margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .deliverable-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 1px; background: var(--color-border); border: 1px solid var(--color-border); }
  .deliverable-card { background: var(--color-surface); padding: 1.5rem; transition: background 200ms; }
  .deliverable-card:hover { background: var(--color-surface-2); }
  .deliverable-title { font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: 500; color: var(--color-text); margin-bottom: 0.4rem; }
  .deliverable-desc { font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--color-text-muted); line-height: 1.6; margin: 0; max-width: none; }
  .body-text { font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--color-text-muted); max-width: 65ch; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0; }
  .tools-list { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 0.4rem; }
  .tool-tag { font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.72rem; color: var(--color-text-muted); border: 1px solid var(--color-border); padding: 0.25rem 0.6rem; border-radius: var(--radius-sm); }
  .service-sidebar { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 2rem; position: sticky; top: 5rem; }
  .sidebar-block { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.6rem; }
  .sidebar-label { font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: 0.62rem; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 0.15em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--color-text-faint); }
  .sidebar-price { font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 300; color: var(--color-text); margin: 0; }
  .sidebar-note { font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--color-text-faint); line-height: 1.5; margin: 0; max-width: none; }
  .sidebar-cta { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.75rem; }
  .sidebar-btn { width: 100%; justify-content: center; }
  @media (max-width: 900px) { .service-body-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } .service-sidebar { position: static; } .deliverable-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
</style>
